TextEng: I would speak with you... and perhaps more.
Me talk with yous? Maybe more?
Goodbye.
<StartAction>Bemoan about how no one really respects you.</Start>
Let's talk about you, and what you like.
You listen well? Does talking make your "clients" more relaxed?
Text: 당신은 잘 들어 주나요? 손님들이 대화를 하면 더 편해지던가요?

TextEng: Perhaps I could ask some serious questions?
Text: 어쩌면 좀 진지한 질문을 해도 될까요?

TextEng: We talk about you. You pretty.
You listen? Talking make customers feel more happy?
Text: 너 잘 들어? 말하면 손님들 기분 좋아져?

TextEng: Maybe me ask serious stuffs, okay?
Where are you from? What is your story?
Where you from? What your story?
Text: 너 어디서 왔어? 무슨 사연 있어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I'd find it degrading to disguise my true self like that.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 난 내 진짜 모습을 속이는 건 스스로를 비하하는 일이라고 생각해요.

TextEng: I want to talk about something else.
Me talk about different things.
<StartAction>Lament the inherent loneliness of the adventurer lifestyle.</Start>
Nothing bothers me. I am strong.
Me strong. Nothing hurt me.
Whatever, harlot. I'm not here to talk.
Text: 됐어, 창녀. 난 이야기하러 온 게 아니야.

TextEng: Shaddap. Me not here for words, lap-lady.
Text: 닥쳐. 나 말하러 온 거 아냐, 무릎 아가씨.

TextEng: There's more than talking, right?
We not just talk, right?
Here is a Pass Coin. My name is <FirstName>.
Here my Pass Coin. Me called <FirstName>.
I don't have a Pass Coin.
Me not gots Pass Coin.
I should be going.
Me should go, maybe.
I'll stay a while, I think.
Text: 조금 더 머물러도 될 것 같네요.

TextEng: Me not so dumb. Me stay.
I must leave. Farewell.
Me gots to go. Bye.
Perhaps we could... retire to your bedchambers, my lady?
Maybe we go sleep now? Nicely, I mean.
Text: 이제 같이 잘래? 좋은 뜻으로 말한 거야.

TextEng: Let's knock boots, honey!
Let's make two-butt beast!
What do you know of the plague?
Know anything about plague?
Shouldn't you be ashamed of working here?
Text: 여기서 일하는 걸 부끄럽게 여겨야 하는 거 아닌가요?

TextEng: You feel dirty? Maybe ashamed?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> That's very selfless, giving of yourself like that.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그렇게 자신을 내어주는 건 참 이타적이네요.

TextEng: A prostitute with a heart of gold. Oh, that's new.
Lap-lady with the heart of gold. That really new.
Text: 마음씨 고운 무릎 아가씨라니. 진짜 새롭네.

TextEng: Don't make me go upside your head!
<StartAction>Confide that you might have a big role in curing the plague.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>자신이 역병 치료에 큰 역할을 맡을지도 모른다고 은밀히 털어놓습니다.</Start>

TextEng: I enjoyed our time together. I hope you did as well.
Text: 함께한 시간이 즐거웠어요. 당신도 그랬으면 합니다.

TextEng: Me like you. Hope you like me a little.
Text: 나 너 좋았어. 너도 조금은 좋았길.

TextEng: Another notch on my sword, woman. Nothing more.
Text: 내 칼자루에 새겨질 또 하나의 눈금일뿐. 그 이상은 아니야.

TextEng: You just one more for the road. Ha!
Text: 넌 그냥 하나 더 추가야. 하!
